# Terminology and product context

## Stack and overview

AI site builder: prompt → own-engine codegen (default) → preview → deploy (Vercel).

**Stack:** Next.js 16 App Router, React 19, TS 5.9, Tailwind 4, shadcn/ui; OpenAI via AI SDK (own engine); Drizzle + Postgres (Supabase); Redis; Stripe; Vercel Blob. Env: `src/lib/config.ts`, `docs/ENV.md`.

**Architecture:** `User → Builder UI → src/lib/gen (own engine) → files → Preview → Deploy`. v0 SDK (templates/registry/zip) is **not** the main codegen stream.

**Key paths:** `src/app/builder/`, `src/app/api/v0/` (routes + legacy v0 API), `src/lib/gen/`, `src/lib/templates/` (v0-templates), `src/components/builder/`, `src/lib/builder/`, `src/lib/hooks/`, `src/lib/db/`, `src/lib/auth/`, `src/proxy.ts` (auth/CORS/headers). Hub: `docs/architecture/README.md`.

**Builder flow:** `ChatInterface` → optional `/api/ai/chat` → orchestration → scaffold → `prepareGenerationContext` → SSE stream → autofix/parse → `PreviewPanel`.

**DB:** Main app tables + own-engine tables (`engine_*`). **Conventions:** Swedish UI copy, English code; `@/*` → `src/*`.

## Layers (do not collapse)

| Layer | Role |
|-------|------|
| **Vercel** | Hosting |
| **Sajtmaskin** | App; own-engine default |
| **v0** | templates/registry/zip; **not** builder codegen streams; optional `V0_FALLBACK_BUILDER` prefers v0 `demoUrl` in preview |
| **Demo sites** | User sites; “demo URL” usually means our preview/deploy, not legacy `*.vusercontent.net` |

