## Aliases → canonical

Varicell / Vericell → **Vercel**. Veenol / Venol → **v0**.

## semantics vs semantic vs embedding

HTML **semantik** ≠ ML **semantisk sökning** / **inbäddning**; code identifiers stay English.

## Legacy docs

Older plans may mention a removed Cursor multi-agent orchestrator — not part of product runtime.

## Own-engine pipeline (rough)

prompt assist → orchestration → scaffold → `orchestrate.ts` → `system-prompt.ts` → stream → autofix/merge. **Custom instructions:** `defaults.ts` — CORE always; EXTENDED when scaffold `off`.

## Theme vs Figma vs v0 DS

`designTheme` / `themeColors` ≠ Figma attachment ≠ `v0DesignSystemId` — do not conflate.

## Project / chat / version

DB project + chats + file snapshots; preview URL; optional legacy v0 IDs.

## Preview and deploy

**Preview:** in-app Next preview; optional v0 `demoUrl` if fallback; degraded env placeholders in `config/ai_models/` + `user_degraded_env.txt`; Sandbox = opt-in server test.

**Deploy:** version files → images → Vercel API → URL.

